</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-72">These are important result. In most of the situations, we are required to analyze motion in linear direction i.e. one direction. In that case, we are required to analyze force, momentum etc in that direction only. This is a great simplification of analysis paradigm as we shall find out in solving problems.
</para>
